@startuml use_cases
left to right direction

actor Player

usecase Start
usecase MovePiece
usecase Bet
usecase RollDice
usecase Resume
usecase Exit

usecase ShowMenu

Player --> Start
Start ..> ShowMenu : <include>
Player --> MovePiece
MovePiece ..> ShowMenu : <extend>
Player --> Bet
Bet ..> ShowMenu : <extend>
Bet ..> Resume : <extend>
Player --> RollDice
RollDice ..> ShowMenu : <include>
MovePiece ..> Resume : <extend>
Resume ..> Start : <extend>
Player --> Exit

@enduml